Definition: offensively curious or inquisitive
Example: curious about the neighbor's doings; he flipped through my letters in his nosy way; prying eyes; the snoopy neighbor watched us all day
Synonyms: noun, communication, nose, cognition, nosiness, nosey, prying, snoopy, person, snoop, snoopiness, offensively, curious, or, inquisitive, about, the, neighbor, s, doings, he, flipped, through, my, letters, in, his, way, eyes, watched, us, all, day
Category: adj.all
